The '''Doohickey''' is a special resource that can be acquired only by [[Winona]] with the [[Founder's Keepers I]] skill. It drops from [[Cachebox]]es after fixing or opening them. Doohickies cannot be seen by other players and can only store in Winona's inventory. If dropped on the ground, it will disappear after a couple of seconds.

The only usage of Doohickey is to craft the [[W.I.N.bot]].

